Rating: 4
Delicious and simple. I recommend "French Picnic" brand crust; it comes in flat rounds, easy to form into tarte pan. Serve with a tablespoon of unsweetened whipped cream to balance the sweetness of the tarte. This will become a staple in my dessert repertoire.

